!=========================================================!
! Input for calculation with the ONETEP program           !
!                                                         !
! Quality Control file for:                               !
! Implicit auto solvation with EDFT.                      !
! This tests the correctness of EDFT restarts at the      !
! boundary between in-vacuum and in-solvent stages.       !
!                                                         !
! Test system: Pt13 in OBCs, borrowed from QC #29.        !
! KE cutoff has been increased to make it easier for MG.  !
